            <title>2.5.0</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 23:22:23 +0545</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/kshitijsubedi/nepali-calendar-mac-updates/raw/refs/heads/main/versions/nepali-calendar-mac-2.5.0-31.dmg</link>
            <sparkle:version>31</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.5.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.1</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## What's New in 2.5.0

### New Settings Window
Proper settings window with sidebar navigation, visual theme picker with live preview, and menu bar style previews.

### Event Management
Create, edit, and delete calendar events directly from the app. Redesigned event list with colored borders, time columns, and gradient backgrounds.

### Calendar Filtering
Choose which system calendars to show. Toggle individual calendar sources on or off.

### Swipe & Navigate
Swipe left or right to change months. Use arrow keys to navigate and ⌘T to jump back to today.
]]></description>
